{"type": "article", "id": 7633, "title": "Yu ito 五彩缤纷的折叠家具", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-23T07:06:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052348390B5jzvcIpJL3aHUO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t春天来了，一切都变得五彩缤纷起来。日本设计师 Yu ito 给意大利家居品牌设计了一套叫做 Linito 的系列家具，折叠的风格本身具有日本传统文化“折纸”的要素，而钢片是现代化的产物，再加上活泼靓丽的色彩，整套家具看上去舒适又愉快。<a href=\"https://www.formabilio.com/shop/design-chairs/chairs/contemporary-chair-linito\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>，感兴趣的话你可以点进来看看。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052348369kTqd6blC1PntufV.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234837z8ZuTdVXlbg9y2QS.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234837P5DgTEJcKYhUrdnZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234837XZN8RH9Wt5reyTan.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234838CIkNwUGhEHbgzoJ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margi